{"tid":1010461,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大年初一！麥當勞唔畀飲筒我點飲呀？","createTime":"2019-02-06T04:15:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-06T05:44:11.000Z","uid":59837,"like":5,"dislike":45,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"458dfbd29241602eb334f5f96907e3748aba2c81","tid":1010461,"uid":59837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T04:15:25.000Z","msg":"話說琴日係大年初一<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n食乜撚嘢麥當勞呀！Hi你老！<br />\n一年得一次嘅農曆新年！好心就食好少少啦！<br />\n唔好同我講冇嘢食點點點！<span style=\"color: red;\">冇咪喺屋企煮囉！</span><br />\n又唔撚等得！又要食！等得耐又要屌！<br />\n再唔係就係拜年食人啲嘢囉！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">事發經過</span></span><br />\n<br />\n狗男女<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：喂，飲筒冇飲筒我哋點飲呢請問？<br />\n<br />\n我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：唔好意思呀先生！其實依家全線餐廳都⋯⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n然後我都未L講完，佢兩個對眼就望撚住我<br />\n<br />\n然後佢哋再講多次<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「下！咁我點飲」</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">然後！</span><br />\n我就好認真咁拎起我杯可樂！<span style=\"color: violet;\">俾個窿佢睇</span>！<br />\n<br />\n圖片是咁的：<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/02/06/d2sqok.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F02%2F06%2Fd2sqok.jpeg&h=a30dd2b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實仲有好多例子<br />\n什麼小朋友冇飲筒飲唔到，我Hi你老母呀？<br />\n小朋友同廢老飲乜撚凍飲呀？飲返熱飲喇！<br />\n<br />\n為咗支飲筒嘈喧巴閉！<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我柒都唔信你喺屋企用飲筒飲水</span><br />\n<br />\n冇得派嘅 咪當支持下環保囉港燦！"},{"pid":"34d97ca5a2f2b0b4c8d5547b47de36c56826efcb","tid":1010461,"uid":59837,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T04:18:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a50b28fa96eaaa69646a92fbcdddcdd6d3e994d1","tid":1010461,"uid":190540,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T04:21:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"aba4d9f606babe54980faa8d727880f8a7430298","tid":1010461,"uid":59837,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"a50b28fa96eaaa69646a92fbcdddcdd6d3e994d1","tid":1010461,"uid":190540,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T04:21:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T04:21:53.000Z","msg":"係 問就有<br />\n留意返佢嘅問題係 冇飲筒點飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而唔係問我拎飲筒"},{"pid":"c3918c29c045881c4eeef5eaa1ad4d4273c17b74","tid":1010461,"uid":190540,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T04:23:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"648b4d60a8bf1ee53d5808f62615860c549a511d","tid":1010461,"uid":59837,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"c3918c29c045881c4eeef5eaa1ad4d4273c17b74","tid":1010461,"uid":190540,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T04:23:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T04:24:07.000Z","msg":"下次我會建議客人飲返熱飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">或者 叫佢咪撚飲</span>"},{"pid":"19e44370a98c65e895883fab11bfda88ed683121","tid":1010461,"uid":41944,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T04:24:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VvE3kCh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVvE3kCh.jpg&h=4438011c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n就係你班仆街，搞到依家出街都要自備即用即棄飲筒"},{"pid":"4873694237eabe3f062c96525774917dab8669be","tid":1010461,"uid":27664,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T04:30:34.000Z","msg":"要學識講外賣但堂食 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44a66f5c723b5f4f19a61cf21dbeba406eca5c92","tid":1010461,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T04:37:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i2-kknew